                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Spanish inclusion in the Western defense community, including <gloss
                        target="#t_NAT1">NATO</gloss>, was discussed at the Western European
                    Ambassadors Conference at Frankfurt on February 5, 1951. For documentation, see
                    Documents 74 ff.</p>
